Merge pull request #1192 from wh1100717/master

Delete CNAME in Master Branch

Delete CNAME in Master Branch

CNAME is mainly used for custom domain with Github Pages. CNAME should
be put in the root of Master branch ONLY when the repository is a `User
Page Site` like `username.github.io`. Otherwise, it should be in the
root of `gh-pages` Branch.
